OL,3,CMan admits murder of woman who
OL,4,Cdisappeared after leaving work
OL,6,FA man has pleaded guilty to the murder
OL,7,Fof a woman who was stabbed to death.
OL,9,FAlireza Askari, 42, admitted murdering
OL,10,FParia Veisi, 37, during a hearing at
OL,11,FCardiff Crown Court on Thursday.
OL,13,FMs Veisi was last seen alive leaving
OL,14,Fwork in April last year and was found
OL,15,Fdead at a property in the Penylan area
OL,16,Fof the city.
OL,18,FAskari, of Penylan, Cardiff, has also
OL,19,Fpleaded guilty to preventing the
OL,20,Flawful and decent burial of a body.
