OL,3,CMan admits murder of woman who
OL,4,Cdisappeared after leaving work
OL,6,FHis co-defendant, Maryam Delavary, 48,
OL,7,Fof Australia Road, White City Estate,
OL,8,Fwest London, previously pleaded guilty
OL,9,Fto perverting the course of justice.
OL,11,FSouth Wales Police said Ms Veisi was
OL,12,Freported missing after leaving her
OL,13,Fworkplace in the Canton area of
OL,14,FCardiff on April 12 2025.
OL,16,FAn inquest opening in May last year
OL,17,Fheard the provisional cause of death
OL,18,Fwas stab wounds to the neck and upper
OL,19,Fchest.
